Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.43,0:00:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗\N在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.57,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传奇故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.54,0:00:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据在北条同学家里\N找到的家谱记载
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的祖先北条秋时的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字竟然叫做戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人难道是指我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world（暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.85,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.75,0:01:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.03,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我  及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.84,0:01:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.94,0:01:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go in and try（不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.38,0:01:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.99,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to Cry\N（同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight\N（直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.43,0:01:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说四魂之玉\N能够实现所有的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找四处飞散的\N四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.19,0:02:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我透过了隐藏在\N神社当中的秘密古井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来回回往返于战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.56,0:02:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除此之外的时间\N我会回到现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当一个普通的国中生\N在学校上课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须很努力应付各种考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学校的同学们\N完全不知道这件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算我说出来\N恐怕也没有人会相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  根本都不会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  停笔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来对历史还很有信心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试范围还是战国时代耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的打击…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你最近常常请假\N不会写也是没有办法的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要补考…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能也要和你一起补考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天来上课啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体的状况好点了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说  日暮同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了一个很特别的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.23,0:03:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们北条家代代相传的家谱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里\N大概在五百年前的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的一位祖先\N北条秋时的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看她叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着“戈薇”耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶\N跟我一模一样的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第137话\N祖先的名字叫做戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学的祖先里面\N竟然有人叫做北条篱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人吓一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果戈薇能够跟那个\N不良男朋友分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟北条同学在一起的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的成为另一个北条篱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那不是家谱\N而是预言书喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学\N可能就是这么想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你觉得呢  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史…得好好的念一念了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这个的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次文化祭拍的照片\N已经洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得不错耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶  戈薇看起来好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连真正的妖怪都拍进去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小兄弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把包袱留下  然后给我滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢反抗的话有的是苦头吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把值钱的东西全都交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是太嚣张的话\N可是会被厌恶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说话的口气\N听起来很像是在打劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三兄弟本来就是在打劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻了  快把钱交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被纠缠不清啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几位是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来还不错嘛  秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  还有犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很谢谢你们\N在危急的时候救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这个对身体很好\N请尝尝看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你来这里干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个说来话长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拜访巫女枫婆婆\N因为有事情想请教她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你是来找枫婆婆的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要请教她事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你此次的旅行\N是为了要完成使命的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们北条家有一把\N名为“乾坤薙刀”的长刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.52,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一把刀柄上下\N各有一把刀身的妖刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我们北条家灾祸不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这些灾祸的源头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就是因为\N这把乾坤薙刀的刀刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种说不出的不祥之气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  快收起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你清醒一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差一点就要被附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要镇住这把刀上的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在刀上\N进行驱邪的仪式就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如你们所见\N这把刀的力量太强大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来  听说可以去白灵山\N消除掉它的邪气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我被赋予这样的一个使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那座山已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说就在最近\N白灵山发生天地异变的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整座山完全崩塌瓦解\N连旧有的痕迹都找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把刀刃的邪气镇住的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾难就会不断地\N降临到我们北条家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你来这里是为了问我\N有没有其他的好方法是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以枫婆婆您的智慧\N应该想得到比较好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会长途跋涉来请教您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那座山峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山峰的深处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一座以灵验闻名的\N名为风雷神社的寺庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里进行镇刀仪式的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪气应该会自然而然地被驱除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风雷神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是这一带最灵验的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只知道是在山峰的深处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要找起来很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山峰的东方有一条河流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着那条河逆流而行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会遇到\N一条名为升云的瀑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.97,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风雷神社\N就在那条瀑步的旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升云瀑步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N请各位一定要跟我一同前往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也知道\N我刚才又被强盗打劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实自从这把刀在我手上以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不断发生灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们  请帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋时是我的家臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助家臣摆脱困境\N这也是主人的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇差不多也该回来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说戈薇姑娘她也会来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  有没有忘记带什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我连教科书都带着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在那边也可以读书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万无一失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次病假的理由\N就说是由于撞到头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以丧失记忆好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  丧失记忆似乎有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蚋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N就说得了猫咪过敏症怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然就说驱魔时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心中了下过诅咒的毒\N而无法动弹  怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  便当来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.72,0:09:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N猫跟毒哪一种理由比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两种都不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点来吧  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.75,0:09:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是北条同学的祖先北条秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  这算不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  说好要带给你的忍者食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越…越南风味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还找到了新产品喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在闹别扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因为\N我们不去找四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却要帮秋时的忙\N所以让他觉得很不高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个心胸狭窄的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.91,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的在闹别扭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在闹别扭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是在闹别扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我已经听枫婆婆说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条现在很困扰嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够帮他的忙不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那四魂之玉碎片该怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被奈落先抢走\N也无所谓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话这么说是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢\N这次是因为白灵山崩塌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条才没有办法\N完成他的使命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白灵山的山崩\N明明是奈落造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能放着\N有困难的人不管啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是人太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  戈薇姑娘真的好善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然戈薇都这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只好带你去那个\N什么瀑步神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把你的事情解决掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么不坦率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上小心啊  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您母亲做的佳肴\N我会好好享用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去\N那座山峰的山脚下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快骑到背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那戈薇姑娘他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有犬夜叉可以背我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒的脚程也很快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  先走一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我们也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要牢牢的抓紧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条  不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N戈薇姑娘的笑容真的好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是北条同学的祖先吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学给我看的家谱上\N的确写着戈薇这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.28,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指我回不了现代\N然后就和那北条结婚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.82,0:12:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河流  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是\N从山峰的东面流出来的河吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你从来就没有想过\N把那把刀给扔掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾难就会降临到\N我们家以外的人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要驱除\N这把刀的妖气才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到北条你这么有男子气概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是犬夜叉你才真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就弱不禁风\N少在那打肿脸充胖子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的太过分了吧  犬夜叉\N你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是  我…我还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有茶屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  那边有间茶屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木屐带…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这么不吉利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是把给人带来灾难的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还要休息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样\N我只要跟人类在一起就觉得头痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人怎么可能\N可以和你的蛮力相提并论嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类可都是血肉之躯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  这个丸子真的好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.03,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条…你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样子贴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了  戈薇的忍者道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘  那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降温用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想刚好可以用这个来冰敷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的越来越凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好了不起耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是便当耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.60,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个煎蛋好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用煮的食物味道也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我还是比较喜欢\N用开水泡的忍者食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我也不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  饭团  等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是把招来不幸的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是带那把刀在身上\N就会招来不幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的情况  你们也都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.07,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很多不幸的事\N都接连而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是心理作用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.48,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把乾之刃就是这样\N会给持刀人带来不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接连不断的小灾祸是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样接踵而来\N是很辛苦的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把刀是妖刀\N不是人类该有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接扔掉还比较省事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条用他自己的方式\N很拼命要完成使命耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他的力量再小\N坐云母身上再怎么头晕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一直在努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就不能给他一点力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要袒护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有袒护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上能够使用妖刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有妖怪\N跟像我这样的半妖而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们来说是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本就不是人类\N可以解决的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本就不懂嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成使命之前也要先注意健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧  秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  真是感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  承蒙您的好意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大堆岩石滚过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.42,0:17:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我闻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火药的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看  天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是鸟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像是风筝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从来没有看过\N那么奇怪的风筝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条  危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然搬得起这么巨大的岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙的目的\N是乾之刃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最后的炸药\N好像就是瞄准秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾之刃所招来的灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说过好几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交出去就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.97,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人这么想要这把刀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示\N敌人绝对拥有坤之刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说“坤之刃”?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为它的力量太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会特地被分成两把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.05,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避讳乾之刃和坤之刃\N两把刀合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会被分开到南北两家\N各自拥有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中的一把\N就是交到了我们北条家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是两把合一的话\N到底会怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜详细的情况\N并没有被流传下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人怀念的重逢\N犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事啊  冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为白灵山崩塌后\N刀刀齐就说了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.00,0:20:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那座灵山\N封印了许许多多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定\N灰刃坊留下的其中一个刀具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.97,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“乾坤薙刀”会因而复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很担心事情会变成那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灰刃坊所打造的妖刀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望犬夜叉少爷\N能够将它再次封印住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就来找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要找我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“只有那家伙办得到了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是刀刀齐要我转告你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.20,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是说“哼”的时候了\N犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这次妄想得到乾之刃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖忍的首领“星黄泉”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说妖忍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖忍是一种\N会使用忍术的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这个星黄泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.39,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是委托灰刃坊\N打造乾坤薙刀的罪魁祸首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说破魔之箭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就可以到风雷神社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没得到教训  又来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是乾之刃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条  快到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.83,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条  你撑着点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.83,0:21:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  秋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.65,0:22:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.22,0:22:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.24,0:22:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.70,0:23:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.68,0:23:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.22,0:23:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是要抢乾之刃的星黄泉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.66,0:23:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这把妖刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事跟你一点关系都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有必要向你解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.56,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在使用可怕的妖忍术的\N这些妖忍的攻击之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟北条\N被迫与犬夜叉他们分散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.54,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到只有我跟戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人被困在\N前往风雷神社的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们两个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.41,0:24:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪山河\N两人的生存之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说\N这就是所谓不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


